 />\n人哋講明係獨立編採<br />\n課金係不帶任何條件"},{"pid":"129b10fc1aee5a9d54b1ee447407f780fd29dc35","tid":2212494,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"3abac61da949083c327b16edaede8285af55b623","tid":2212494,"uid":236140,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c477a5d8aed10602adf7dbc46bbcccd9617a7511","tid":2212494,"uid":51469,"like":12,"dislike":11,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff99614ee4e4904cfc0245864bf4bca29c50cd6c","tid":2212494,"uid":236140,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T02:15:28.000Z","msg":"港產片搵楊明拍你又睇咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵錯演員就抵屌！"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T02:19:25.000Z","msg":"幻愛一樣有政府科水<br />\n你唔批鬥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T02:26:08.000Z","msg":"咁咪即係我哋啲錢囉！你無交過稅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T02:46:32.000Z","msg":"咁就唔係奶共呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比錢睇又唔係科水？"},{"pid":"0572790d7565fb49f9c4609efd739cf90f271f9a","tid":2212494,"uid":272652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T02:48:26.000Z","msg":"佢地靠賺稿費過日子，由個班柒頭影評玩啦，我地唔睇咪得囉"},{"pid":"ce0406c790c71fd6acd9fa1ad220ebf618ca3d03","tid":2212494,"uid":228995,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T02:50:40.000Z","msg":"你班人第一日睇立場？<br />\n<br />\n一向好多影評都會投稿立場"},{"pid":"337bc96d376a141fa981ecc1dae09d2118acee09","tid":2212494,"uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T03:14:31.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">食屎啦屌你老母立場新聞</span></span>"},{"pid":"7f4837260adf18b9fe1f9d4f6db44797c1ec3a60","tid":2212494,"uid":15213,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c477a5d8aed10602adf7dbc46bbcccd9617a7511","tid":2212494,"uid":51469,"like":12,"dislike":11,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff99614ee4e4904cfc0245864b